CECIL A. GAINES, CARL FRANKLIN and WALTER S. COLLINS v. STATE OF FLORIDA. 22 So. (2nd) 155

January Term, 1945

May 11, 1945 Division B W. W. Flournoy, for appellant. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, and Reeves Bowen, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The judgment appealed from is affirmed.

It is so ordered.

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
